Company Profile
Sector: Financials
Industry: Asset Management
Sub-Industry: Investment Management
World Funds Trust/USA was founded in 2009. The company's line of business includes the management of funds, trusts, and foundations organized for purposes other than religious, educational, charitable, or nonprofit research.




